<body>
    <header>
        <h1>W.D. Missouri Bankruptcy — Empirical Court Research</h1>
        <p>Empirical research on the U.S. Bankruptcy Court for the Western District of Missouri: judges, trustees, attorneys, dismissal rates, and case patterns from PACER data.</p>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h2>About this site</h2>
        <p>This satellite hosts empirical research on the <strong>U.S. Bankruptcy Court for the Western District of Missouri</strong> derived from PACER docket data.</p>
        <p>Pages under construction:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/judges/">5 judges &mdash; profile pages with judicial positions and primary-source links</a></li>
            <li><a href="/trustees/">Trustee reference</a> &mdash; Sub V, standing Ch. 13, US Trustee, with CourtListener search paths</li>
            <li>/attorneys/&mdash; firm-level pattern profiles</li>
            <li>/dismissal-rates/&mdash; chapter-level dismissal data</li>
            <li>/discharge-rates/&mdash; chapter-level discharge data</li>
            <li>/data/&mdash; raw CSV/JSON exports</li>
        </ul>
        <hr>
        <p><strong>Source data:</strong> see <a href="https://openbankruptcyproject.org/cases/mowbk/">Open Bankruptcy Project /cases/mowbk/</a> for the underlying district profile pages.</p>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>Hosted by <a href="https://openbankruptcyproject.org/">Open Bankruptcy Project</a>, a 501(c)(3) public charity (EIN 41-5159631). Empirical research only &mdash; not legal advice.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
